# --- Laravel Core (Quét mọi thư mục con) ---
**/vendor/
**/node_modules/
**/.env
**/.env.backup
**/.env.production
**/public/build/
**/public/hot/
**/public/storage/
**/storage/*.key
**/storage/pail/

# --- Laravel Storage Logs & Cache (Bổ sung) ---
**/storage/logs/*.log
**/storage/framework/cache/data/
**/storage/framework/sessions/
**/storage/framework/testing/
**/storage/framework/views/

# --- Testing & Caches ---
**/.phpunit.cache/
**/.phpunit.result.cache
**/npm-debug.log
**/yarn-error.log
**/.vite-inspect

# --- IDEs & Editors Configuration ---
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/.fleet/
**/.nova/
**/.zed/
**/.phpactor.json

# --- Environment Packages & Miscellaneous ---
**/Homestead.json
**/Homestead.yaml
**/auth.json
**/*.sql

# --- OS Files (Bổ sung) ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini